[Guest]: know it's the love jihad of that time if you like but it was not conflictual in the sense that is

03:11:31.800 --> 03:11:38.840
[Guest]: being made out and then it was it was a periphery that got into the act and the violence broke out

03:11:39.400 --> 03:11:44.920
