03:12:08.440 --> 03:12:15.560
[Guest]: work who are trying to generate a viciousness within us who are trying to generate hate within

03:12:15.560 --> 03:12:22.840
[Guest]: us who are using hate speech as the currency as their currency so unless we no one are able to

03:12:22.840 --> 03:12:28.440
[Guest]: catch that and the police often don't tell you about it or project it right or even prosecute it

03:12:29.000 --> 03:12:34.600
[Guest]: because there's a there's a infiltration there so you have to be alive to all of this and there

03:12:34.600 --> 03:12:39.400
