03:16:39.160 --> 03:16:44.360
[Guest]: that time was to distribute to journalists this map of ahemdabad which was painted

03:16:44.360 --> 03:16:49.800
[Guest]: uh orange and green and i'm looking everywhere my people come a hoarder when i'm a real archivist

