03:17:26.760 --> 03:17:32.280
[Guest]: sari-clad women had pushed him to his death from the second floor back it was something that chilled

03:17:32.280 --> 03:17:39.720
[Guest]: me because it was like so many things in that incident because it it was and how do you and how

03:17:39.720 --> 03:17:45.720
[Guest]: do you ensure that a community remains ghettoized and the brutality of the violence the fact that

03:17:45.720 --> 03:17:50.920
[Guest]: women are now engaging in communal violence as much as men which was not something i saw till 86

03:17:50.920 --> 03:17:58.120
[Guest]: 87 in the country at all so you saw the handiwork of the vishwa hindu parishad and the sadhvi

03:17:58.120 --> 03:18:03.880
[Guest]: then the sadhvi ritambaras as as icons you know it's working it's working in society so it was

03:18:03.880 --> 03:18:10.760
[Guest]: horrific at so many levels so anyway i was in the process of writing this book so i was speaking in

03:18:10.760 --> 03:18:15.960
[Guest]: nagpur and this is i think just a few months before the book came out in 2016 and there's a

03:18:15.960 --> 03:18:20.120
[Guest]: public meeting in nagpur where i narrated this incident and i write about this also in the book

03:18:21.160 --> 03:18:26.520
[Guest]: and after the meeting is over on the stage and all if you remember i see this young man sitting

03:18:26.520 --> 03:18:31.400
[Guest]: there and he's shaken really shaken right and he said ma'am can i have a word with you and all i

03:18:31.400 --> 03:18:37.240
[Guest]: said sure and he's he's a reporter for the times of india won't mention his name and he said i just

03:18:37.240 --> 03:18:44.200
[Guest]: want to finish your story you mentioned that incident and i was just 12 or 13 or 14 when it

03:18:44.200 --> 03:18:49.320
[Guest]: took place and it had chilled me and my family and i don't think you know this because you've

03:18:49.320 --> 03:18:54.440
[Guest]: reported gujarat so closely i'm telling you so you can round off the story that that navratri

03:18:54.440 --> 03:19:02.760
[Guest]: three months later those women were felicitated so you know you realize when you're writing coming

03:19:02.760 --> 03:19:07.480
[Guest]: back to your earlier question that how do you write these stories that you have to write about

03:19:07.480 --> 03:19:13.640
[Guest]: every nuance and every tone if you're honest about the story you have to also write the fact

03:19:13.640 --> 03:19:20.040
[Guest]: that when you reach godhra the first time i reached godhra godhra was on 21st 22nd of

03:19:20.040 --> 03:19:28.840
