03:19:36.360 --> 03:19:41.960
[Guest]: and you have to actually unravel those rumors so the rumor was one rumor for the majority

03:19:41.960 --> 03:19:46.600
[Guest]: community one rumor for the minority community all of that because you know by then you had tv

03:19:46.600 --> 03:19:51.400
[Guest]: internet emails had begun and all of that and one particular story i remember was about this

03:19:52.520 --> 03:20:00.600
[Guest]: muslim girl at the godhra platform who was eve-teased by the karsevaks okay so that incident

03:20:00.600 --> 03:20:05.080
[Guest]: happened it was bakrid that she was returned bakrid i was few days back so she was returning

03:20:05.080 --> 03:20:11.000
[Guest]: to baroda with her mother and her younger sister and she was in attractive teenager and she was

03:20:11.000 --> 03:20:15.080
[Guest]: actually eve-teased but what did the rumor among the muslim community say that she was pulled inside

03:20:15.080 --> 03:20:21.160
[Guest]: one of the compartments and something so you know the story becomes another story you know so one

03:20:21.160 --> 03:20:26.760
[Guest]: of the things i keep saying in my lectures to journalists and suggestions is never report

03:20:26.760 --> 03:20:32.680
[Guest]: incidents of communal violence unless you have verified every incident even of the survivor or

03:20:32.680 --> 03:20:38.600
[Guest]: the victim because because there is a tendency to of the of the untruth to also spiral into truth

03:20:38.600 --> 03:20:43.000
[Guest]: you know because that's how the rumor functions and rumor is something you have to really guard

03:20:43.000 --> 03:20:50.760
[Guest]: against as a journalist so long winded answer but to say that be honest be truthful cover every nuance

03:20:51.320 --> 03:20:55.320
[Guest]: but never forget that the human victim needs to be central to the story

03:20:57.560 --> 03:21:01.720
[Guest]: victim or survivor because you're not writing about numbers you're not writing about

03:21:01.720 --> 03:21:06.040
[Guest]: numbers of death but you're writing about a human being a set of human beings who've lost their

03:21:06.040 --> 03:21:12.200
[Guest]: dignity and life it is something you learn i don't think anything is just pure instinct or natural

03:21:12.200 --> 03:21:17.000
[Guest]: but it's something i learned because i was serious about continuing to cover it though

03:21:17.000 --> 03:21:20.920
[Guest]: it was a deep personal cost because it takes something out of you every time

