04:05:54.440 --> 04:06:01.400
[Amit Varma]: people you can convict ringleaders as indeed you have right some of them you have some of them yeah

04:06:01.400 --> 04:06:09.480
[Amit Varma]: yeah but the point is everybody participated and that's just such a horrifying thought that

04:06:09.480 --> 04:06:15.400
