04:07:17.480 --> 04:07:23.960
[Guest]: rwanda at that time the 800 000 people massacred so what is it that drives populations to this

04:07:24.600 --> 04:07:30.680
[Guest]: level of an expanse of bestiality and more important as you said how do you recover from

04:07:30.680 --> 04:07:36.040
[Guest]: it how does a society then re-engage with each other and reconstruct i mean it's like

04:07:36.600 --> 04:07:41.880
