04:07:41.880 --> 04:07:49.800
[Guest]: to be through the voices of the survivors who tell us the solutions we cannot cannot in any means

04:07:49.800 --> 04:07:55.400
[Guest]: give a solution to them it has to be a solution that maybe we can help facilitate as sensitive

04:07:55.400 --> 04:07:59.720
[Guest]: human beings but how can we be the ones who give it to them i have no answer to that but i just

04:07:59.720 --> 04:08:05.080
