04:08:09.720 --> 04:08:15.160
[Guest]: didn't happen or by blurring the narrative or turning the narrative on its head or saying that

04:08:15.160 --> 04:08:19.720
[Guest]: you know this is all spontaneous or i mean at least let's engage with the kind of horrors that

04:08:19.720 --> 04:08:24.600
[Guest]: we've been able to at least those that we witness in our lifetimes you know even if partition is

04:08:24.600 --> 04:08:31.640
