04:08:31.640 --> 04:08:37.800
[Guest]: and which community was affected at least what we know is is that that is reasonably true that

04:08:37.800 --> 04:08:43.880
[Guest]: it has happened it's been reported and before anybody kind of accuses me of you know saying

04:08:43.880 --> 04:08:48.040
[Guest]: what i said about naroda bhatt you just have to read the judgment of judge jyotsnaya yagnik

04:08:48.040 --> 04:08:55.640
