04:29:07.080 --> 04:29:11.320
[Guest]: whether it's a high court or a supreme court so i think it's with that hope that you go there

04:29:12.440 --> 04:29:17.560
[Guest]: otherwise you might as well say if you want extends your argument further that you know leave

04:29:17.560 --> 04:29:21.960
[Guest]: aside this battle to the courts wait or don't wait for that day when it happens and fight your battles

04:29:21.960 --> 04:29:26.760
